            "title": "Evaporative water loss in Kuhl's pipistrelles declines along an environmental gradient, from mesic to hyperarid",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Cassandra",
                    "lastName": "Gearhart"
                },
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
